ug_text: Naomi has an innocent, anime school girl appearance that often misleads her enemies into thinking she is of little threat. However, they soon learn their mistake after a swift chainsaw to the face leaves them in pieces.

Knox is perhaps the most misunderstood figure in the Micro World, but underneath that tough exterior there is a heart of gold. He defends himself from hurled insults and flying bullets with his street smarts and heavy build.

Pandora uses her captivating powers of seduction to lure in targets before breaking their little hearts and crushing their souls. It is surely impossible to tame this gothic beauty, but many toys have fallen trying.

C.H.I.P. (Complex Humanoid Interchangeable Parts) was built with spare parts salvaged from a junk yard. He is extremely impatient, without any regard for his own safety. This makes him a highly unpredictable opponent.

Kai was outsourced to a manufacturer in the Far East, but after a long journey, he has finally been reunited with the other prototypes. His tactical awareness and diplomatic skills give him an edge on the playground.
Strong Combat Fighter with +10% Bullet Armor and +100 HP Bonus.
The Zooc Company made her much more beatiful and powerful than she ever be in her original story! [Default Speed +3%, Explosion Armor +10%]
Be a World Star Rapper in MicroVolts. Rap and Beat your opponents from dusk till dawn. Bonus Character stats: HP +200
A sacred warrior. 10% Explosion and Bullet Defense, and 10% Battery Drop Chance.
